data.description:
Charming cottage! $500.00 credit for a home warranty of your choice at closing.   Move-in ready on .50 acres.  Desirable location close to the lake.  Three bedrooms and two full baths.  New luxury vinyl flooring, updated countertops, painted cabinets, new kitchen backsplash,   2-year-old HVAC unit.  Spacious kitchen with room for an island.  The laundry area supports a full-size washer and dryer.  Enjoy your covered back porch and watch the deer wander through the yard.  Lots of room to park your boat or RV.  Newer shed in the back.   
Buyers are to verify all measurements, SF, and schools.  The seller does not have any mineral ownership interest.  
This is a must-see!
